                  <h5 class="modal-title" id="videoVisitLabel">Alcohol use > Record</h5>
                  <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                  <p><strong>Complete questionnaire to generate a score.</strong></p>
                  <div class="form-check">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="declineAll">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="declineAll">Patient declined to specify on all questions</label>
                  </div>
                  <hr>
                  <p>1. How often do you have a drink containing alcohol?</p>
                  <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="drinkFrequency" id="never"><label class="form-check-label" for="never">Never</label></div>
                  <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="drinkFrequency" id="monthly"><label class="form-check-label" for="monthly">Monthly or less</label></div>
                  <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="drinkFrequency" id="2to4"><label class="form-check-label" for="2to4">2–4 times a month</label></div>
                  <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="drinkFrequency" id="2to3week"><label class="form-check-label" for="2to3week">2–3 times a week</label></div>
                  <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="drinkFrequency" id="4plus"><label class="form-check-label" for="4plus">4 or more times a week</label></div>
                  <hr>
                  <p>2. How many standard drinks containing alcohol do you have on a typical day?</p>
